Subject: drm/amd/display: Use DPM table clk setting for dml2 soc dscclk
Git-commit: 15b959534a39530a21d378190557cc8d1eab7b09
Patch-mainline: v6.15-rc1
References: jsc#PED-13979 jsc#PED-14039 jsc#PED-14046 jsc#PED-14211 jsc#PED-14333 jsc#PED-14487 jsc#PED-14488 jsc#PED-14497 jsc#PED-14499

[WHY]
Not like dppclk/dispclk, dml2 will calculate the minimum required clocks.
For dscclk, it is used for pure comparision.

